    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. One factor (Test conditions) is below required level due to single test condition; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of ASTM F1717 and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories.",
